Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.23,0:00:04.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼 明天開始放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:06.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不要玩得太瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.11,0:00:13.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:14.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:18.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天一起去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.62,0:00:21.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}突然想吃西瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那算啥呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去噴西瓜子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.12,0:00:26.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啊好啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,——op——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.98,0:02:08.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 是期盼已久的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:14.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不用上學 我可以玩個盡興啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要好好做作業哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你肯定想著明天是暑假的第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:21.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作業就先放到一邊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被我猜對了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:27.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但不好好享受暑假怎麼行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:32.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一想到要去游泳池 還要去海水浴或者野營之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,時間就完全不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:38.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是一直都是暑假就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:39.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也挺喜歡上學的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:44.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:48.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:55.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.78,0:02:57.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,風吹得好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.74,0:02:59.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再騎快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別為難我了 太熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:16.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們也試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,當然 西片坐前面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 這種事情不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看會遇上汽車什麼的 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但這裡汽車走不了 也不是校道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 難道你害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那你是不會騎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:43.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是 太危險了所以不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:47.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那我們去空地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,如果你失敗了 就要請我喝果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我瞧好了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,區區騎車帶人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 剛剛的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要請果汁了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,騎車帶人有這麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:20.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你沒有故意使絆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:21.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是正常地坐著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,做不到都是西片的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:30.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:32.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,之前我坐別人的自行車的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:34.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個人騎得很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是女性朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 不是女生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:43.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再來一次 就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一次一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:59.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡啊 心裡突然有些不爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才沒有 只是不想請果汁而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒錯 只是我不想請果汁罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哦 前進了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:22.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,最後一次和我兩個人一起騎車的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是我爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好像是四歲的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:36.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片不買果汁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:52.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我…就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不好意思說沒錢給自己買了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正你又打算拿間接接吻什麼的來捉弄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別逞強了 喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:18.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要忍住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種時候需要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給你 別中暑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:31.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可以拿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:31.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片一提到間接接吻就會臉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才不是因為這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:51.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暫時不能一起放學回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是因為暑假到了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:07.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:12.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始 中午之前在這裡練習騎車帶人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼？我倒是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是不可以上公路哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 在這裡騎就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,只在這裡騎的話 練習不就沒有意義了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 有意義哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天開始就是暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好了 那我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真期待暑假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,現在才這麼想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,暑假第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒想到暑假的第一天就下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的暑假計劃全毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:02.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,才一天而已 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,本來要今天去的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼補回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:08.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你別哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然下雨那也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好啦 開始做作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,「誒」什麼啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會沒帶作業過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我不是說了下雨不能出去玩 不如做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:26.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還以為聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:27.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,再說明明是暑假為什麼會有作業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,假日不應該休息才對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:35.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,既然有那也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉也別做作業 一起來癱著無所事事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是眼前有人在做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就會讓我想起作業 根本享受不起來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:00.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,關我啥事 話說你倒是給我想起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這才第一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:05.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作業什麼的就別管了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.11,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是會在8月31日哭的典型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:15.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你這個石頭腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,夠了 我要看漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.46,0:09:25.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以用漫畫來寫閱讀感想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:31.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:34.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你們趕緊給我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太好了 終於天晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:50.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說我在高興什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:56.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:04.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為我們不是約好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:08.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到處都是水窪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,昨晚下大雨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一時間我還沒認出來是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:29.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 雖然在休息日和她也遇過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:32.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,和她約出來玩還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道這就是所謂的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:38.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 才不是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這只是騎車帶人的練習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這樣子沒法練習騎車帶人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.21,0:10:54.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:59.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我原本計劃中午直接出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.80,0:11:03.51,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,回家太麻煩了 到中午之前就陪我打發時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.60,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是…約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:15.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可以啊 不要去人太多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,要是被同級的人看見了 不知道他們會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:23.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很有夏天的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:32.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一般不是晚上玩的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:35.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 裡面還挺黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:41.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且這裡 聽說會出現哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會出現什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:47.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這條隧道本來是直通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:50.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,卻經常發生車輛撞上牆壁的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.44,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這才被迫在旁邊修了一條新的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,從此以後每晚都會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:04.20,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒有了車輛作為獵物的嗜血幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.45,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:09.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這附近還有神隱的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:14.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有時候 人會「呼」的一聲消失不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.63,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你不進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.01,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說 你害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.72,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且現在可是大白天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這種東西一點也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比想像中還要黑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺聽到了奇怪的風聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,符咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這是護身符吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.74,0:12:50.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這裡有些什麼不好的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:54.62,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片你害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 剛剛的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這次又是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,為什麼這裡會有油桶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.14,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去看看裡面有什麼吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,誰怕了 看就看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:17.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我去看總行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:45.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別耍我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:14:00.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來 她剛剛有說過神隱什麼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.49,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 快回話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:18.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你慌什麼呢 是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才在找我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.05,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看上去像是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.09,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡的高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:30.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這就是她的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.22,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,哎 你看那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有一個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.81,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,去看看裡面有什麼吧 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我可不會重複中同樣的招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,別小看我了 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,拔 拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的手拔不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的演技怎麼樣啊高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來吧 害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學 我好像被什麼東西扯住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:57.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快來幫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.46,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西…片…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.29,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被嚇到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:06.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是掉在那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,手 能拔出來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:14.30,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:15.93,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我們走著瞧 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,下一次我一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你太大驚小怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:25.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,出來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:28.82,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,可惡 一次也沒能報復成功
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:30.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 哥哥你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.78,0:15:34.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又有情侶在隧道約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要說了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,他們說是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到底在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:46.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.42,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你的臉好紅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:52.97,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,試膽真好玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,快到中午了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.61,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,又要走那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你害怕嗎 西片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:20.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的份完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.87,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦 明明是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:25.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,俯臥撐的數量卻完全沒少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,自由研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.84,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯 清湯味挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.18,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你騙人 眼淚都要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不不 我覺得比早苗的昆布味好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.43,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,半斤八兩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明明有這麼多口味可以挑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.69,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不明白你們為什麼要選那兩種
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉的西瓜味太沒新意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:48.86,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,正所謂冒險才是青春 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.90,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,選個冰棍也算冒險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:54.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個 你們倆決定好自由研究要做什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:55.78,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,美奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.12,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我也還在考慮中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.25,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有什麼比較輕鬆的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,一天就能做完的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.21,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你倒是好好研究啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,狗的觀察日記如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:15.13,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個不錯 聽上去很簡單的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:17.80,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,反正每天的行動都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,複印後把日期改下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:22.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,至少給我努力用手寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:24.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,而且狗的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不就是吠著要你起床之後帶它去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:29.65,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吠著要你給它餵食 然後睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.74,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,吠著要你陪它玩 然後又吠著要吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,根本沒有研究的意義吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:38.57,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,由加莉真是死板
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:40.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嘛 人家是年級委員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:42.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真拿她沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這兩個傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.50,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說你們 寫作業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.71,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,時間還多得是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話先說在前頭 我不會給你們抄的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:02.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,作為交換 我們幫你做自由研究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:04.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是關於狗的吧 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,雖然你總說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.48,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,到最後還是會借給我們看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.31,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,人家是年級委員嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.56,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:14.28,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我的自由研究就觀察這兩個傢伙好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.36,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,水管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:21.66,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天真是暑假裡最倒霉的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.58,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,早上睡過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.34,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,然後自行車還爆胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.55,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天沒有騎車帶人的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.64,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,高木同學說她和家人去旅行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是今天回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:46.85,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:50.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我難得忍住中午出去玩的衝動幫忙做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還被派去跑腿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.52,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,這暑假真是倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.19,0:18:57.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,今天的一句話日記就這樣寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.32,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.24,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那個背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:05.79,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,已經回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.04,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好 悄悄地跟在她後面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,說不定還能發現她的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:36.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,感覺剛剛她往這邊看了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.99,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不 應該是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.70,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被她發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:44.95,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,但是我看到你的帽子了哦 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你打算嚇唬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:48.91,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那就讓我先發制人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:50.75,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,在一句話日記裡寫上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,中 中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.76,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:04.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,被叫去超市買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.80,0:20:07.89,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真巧啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你載著我一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,都說了 不可以騎車帶人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.02,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.23,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,她什麼時候發現我在跟蹤她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:18.19,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,那一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:20.94,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,小心 高木同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.07,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.32,0:20:28.33,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,果然今天真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.00,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:33.96,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,沒事 這種程度放著不管就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:36.67,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不行 一定要洗一洗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.26,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,太糗了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.06,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,有那麼疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:50.35,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.39,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我只是在想今天本來就運氣差了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.77,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,還受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.15,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是個糟透了的暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:02.53,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,真是的 日記作業要寫什麼才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:03.40,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:07.16,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,會弄髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.83,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.37,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.38,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.47,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,你剛才是想要幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.10,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,西片也過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.73,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,涼涼的很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.27,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:41.98,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:47.03,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,很涼快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:49.41,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.54,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,我覺得今天的暑假很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:21:56.08,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,因為遇到了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:21:59.92,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.59,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,明天給你帶手信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.17,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:06.88,Takagisan-text,,0,0,0,,不要啊高木同學 好涼啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.43,0:00:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,——OPJP——
