Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:41.21,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}昨天的我 宛如一隻幼貓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:46.92,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}隱約還記得 白色的皮毛顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.14,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}顫抖不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:59.06,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}那是我墜入愛河的一天 是我愛上你的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:02.98,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}吶 請不要忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:09.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}墜入愛河的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:14.99,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車去看海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:18.83,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}在拂曉的天空朝太陽奔去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:22.58,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}不需修飾的日子裡繼續聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:30.18,Takagisan-OPEDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,500)}踏上自行車奔向太陽
